'''District 3054''' was an urban district on [[Vorzyd V/Legends|Vorzyd V]]. [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] went through it on his way to rendezvous with [[Natala Vanden]] in [[1 ABY/Legends|1 ABY]]. Skywalker had been surveyed by [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] agent [[O-625]] until losing track of him in 3054. Another group of Imperials quickly dispatched a number of [[AC1 surveillance droid|spy eyes]] which followed Skywalker through the district.

